    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Reaction on your turn, you can take an aggressive stance. </p><p>Until the end of your turn, double your speed and jump distance. </p><p>You gain an additional bonus action, which you can only use to Dash. </p><p>Additionally, when you Dash or Jump, you have advantage on the first taijutsu or weapon attack you make against each creature within range of your weapon where you land or end your movement. </p>",
